chinese new year. if you live in a city with a sizable overseas chinese community, check for cheap flights with someone in that community or visit travel agencies operated by chinese. sometimes flights advertised only in chinese newspapers or travel agencies cost significantly less than posted fares in english. however if you go and ask, you can get the same discount price. see also: discount airlines in asia information: as a result of the h1n1-flu pandemic there are some kinds of health-checks currently in effect. these may be as simple as a customs person judging your appearance to ir-cameras checking 